<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span> حسن - <span class="c2">((صحيح أبي داود)</span>) <span class="c2">(٩٨٠)</span> , <span class="c2">((ابن خزيمة)</span>) <span class="c2">(١٧٢٤)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>